# Canonical host: every other hostname 301s to the real one so search
# engines never see two copies of the site as duplicate content.
# (This is what was blocking Google indexing — www.primeinterestinc.com was
# serving a full 200 OK duplicate of every page instead of redirecting,
# and Google refuses to index either copy of a true duplicate pair.)
https://prime-interest.pages.dev/* https://primeinterestinc.com/:splat 301
https://www.primeinterestinc.com/* https://primeinterestinc.com/:splat 301
